     in controller          controller def create
                              def create
                                @coupon = Coupon.new
                                @coupon.coupon_code = params["coupon_code"] 
                                @coupon.store = params["store"] 
                                @coupon.save
                                redirect_to coupon_path(@coupon)
                              end
    input naming
                            Rails apps use that model[attribute] syntax for name attributes (e.g., post[title])

    inspect form params on same page
